WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.566
Xuerou, you are in such a hurry to find me

2
00:00:02.566 --> 00:00:03.900
What's the matter?

3
00:00:04.066 --> 00:00:05.500
Grandma my dad

4
00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:06.733
He actually did it for a security guard

5
00:00:06.733 --> 00:00:08.366
To cut ties with me

6
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:11.300
You must call the shots for me!

7
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:14.400
Your dad got out of the army

8
00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:18.100
Starting from scratch, standing on top of today's peak

9
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.366
He has his reasons for doing things

10
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:24.066
I don't care if he doesn't recognize me

11
00:00:24.066 --> 00:00:25.433
Then I don't recognize him either.

12
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:29.433
Did you know that your dad has terminal cancer?

13
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:31.966
Not much time

14
00:00:31.966 --> 00:00:34.266
Grandma, what did you say?

15
00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:40.433
Dad, what's the matter with you?

16
00:00:41.566 --> 00:00:42.466
Yeah.

17
00:00:43.066 --> 00:00:43.966
Just a cold

18
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:45.566
Go do your thing

19
00:00:50.866 --> 00:00:53.266
Is Dad really terminal cancer?

20
00:00:53.266 --> 00:00:55.966
So you listen to your dad

21
00:00:55.966 --> 00:00:58.733
Do whatever your dad tells you to do

22
00:00:58.733 --> 00:01:00.266
He can't be wrong.

23
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.866
Ah, good.

24
00:01:03.933 --> 00:01:06.066
Grandma, I get it.

25
00:01:12.966 --> 00:01:14.800
What are you doing here?

